properties.name: _Gadsden Purchase
properties.note:
Gadsden Purchase (1853-12-30)

1853/12/30 -> 1854/08/03

Gadsden Purchase settled the boundary dispute between the United States and Mexico and established the international line at its present location.

(U.S. Stat., vol. 10, pp. 1031-1037; Van Zandt, 11, 29, 162)
